"Linux 5.11 is that a second B<sigaction>()  will clear unknown bits from "
"I<oldact-E<gt>sa_flags>.  However, historically, a second B<sigaction>()  "
"call would typically leave those bits set in I<oldact-E<gt>sa_flags>."
